summary.span: 將多個值的雜湊碼合併成單一雜湊碼。

span.span: Combines the hash code for multiple values into a single hash code.

remarks.format: ## Remarks 您可以使用結合成單一雜湊程式碼的多個值 （例如結構或類別欄位）。You can use to combine multiple values (for example, fields on a structure or class) into a single hash code. 此結構的運作中有兩種：This structure operates in one of two ways: * 接受一組要合併的最多八個值的靜態方法。Static methods that accept a set of up to eight values to combine. * 兩個執行個體中資料流的方式，接受一個值，一次作業的方法。Two instance methods that operate in a streaming fashion, accepting values one at a time. > [!WARNING] > 它是雜湊程式碼視為實作詳細資料，最佳做法，因為實作可能會在組件版本之間變更。It is best-practice to consider hash codes as an implementation detail, as the implementation may change across assembly versions. 不會儲存所產生的雜湊程式碼中序列化的結構，例如，磁碟上。Do not store hash codes produced by in serialized structures, for example, on-disk. 若要強制執行此最佳做法，這表示雜湊程式碼才具有決定性的作業系統處理序的範圍內使用以靜態方式初始化的隨機種子。 uses a statically initialized random seed to enforce this best practice, meaning that the hash codes are only deterministic within the scope of an operating system process. ### 靜態方法Static Methods 靜態方法結合最多八個值的預設雜湊碼。The static methods combine the default hash codes of up to eight values. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#1](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example1.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#1](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example1.vb#1)] ### 執行個體方法Instance Methods > [!IMPORTANT] > 每個執行個體必須最多一次呼叫。 must be called at most once per instance of . 執行個體方法結合超過八個值的雜湊碼。The instance methods combine the hash codes of more than eight values. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#2](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example2.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#2](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example2.vb#1)] 執行個體方法也會合併特定所產生之雜湊碼實作。The instance methods also combine the hash codes produced by a specific implementation. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#3](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example3.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#3](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example3.vb#1)] 結構必須傳遞傳給其他方法，因為它是實值類型。The structure must be passed by-reference to other methods, as it is a value type. [!code-csharp[System.HashCode.Structure#4](~/samples/snippets/csharp/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/cs/example4.cs#1)] [!code-vb[System.HashCode.Structure#4](~/samples/snippets/visualbasic/VS_Snippets_CLR_System/system.hashcode.structure/vb/example4.vb#1)]
